desc: The Tib Tool™ is the affordable solution to training the tibialis muscle. The use of a Tib Bar and Tib Raises was first popularised by Knees Over Toes Guy using the ATG System. Train your tib in order to prevent issues such as shin splints, knee pain, ankle immobility and promote longevity and performance.

layout.text: The solution to training your Tibilais Muscle!
